SYNOPSIS
test [-[no]h] [-[no]quiet] [-[no]version] [-[no]copyright] [-nice <int>] [-[no]backup]
OPTIONS
Other options:
-[no]h (no) Print help and quit -[no]quiet (no) Do not print common startup info or quotes -[no]version (no) Print extended version information and quit -[no]copyright (yes) Print copyright information on startup -nice <int> (19) Set the nicelevel (default depends on command) -[no]backup (yes) Write backups if output files exist
Additional help is available on the following topics: commands List of available commands topic Test topic To access the help, use 'test help <topic>'. For help on a command, use 'test help <command>'.
